| `list-baselines` | List all baselines | `mcp__wundr__drift_detection { action: "list-baselines" }` |
| `trends` | Show drift trends over time | `mcp__wundr__drift_detection { action: "trends" }` |

**Usage Examples:**
```javascript
// Create baseline before major refactoring
mcp__wundr__drift_detection { action: "create-baseline" }

// Check for drift after changes
mcp__wundr__drift_detection { action: "detect" }

// View quality trends
